snippet.title: 33 LGBT Celebs Who Are Couples and You Probably Didn't Know
snippet.description:
LGBTQ couples have had to overcome many challenges. Celebrities who are always in the spotlight have to face these challenges publicly. Here are 33 LGBT celebs who are couples and you probably didn't know because they chose to live their lives as privately as possible.
